2016年8月8日在巴基斯坦[[俾路支省|俾路支省]]首府[[奎达|奎达]]一家公立医院发生自杀式爆炸和枪击的恐怖袭击，结果造成93人死亡，130多人受伤。<ref name=metro6054485>{{cite web |url=http://metro.co.uk/2016/08/08/93-mourners-dead-after-bomb-explodes-at-hospital-in-pakistan-6054485/ |title=93 mourners dead after bomb explodes at hospital in Pakistan |last1=Mann |first1=Tanveer |date=2016-08-08 |website=metro.co.uk |access-date=2016-08-10 |quote= |archive-date=2016-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809155218/http://metro.co.uk/2016/08/08/93-mourners-dead-after-bomb-explodes-at-hospital-in-pakistan-6054485/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>俾路支省律师协会主席比拉勒·安瓦尔·卡西当天早晨在上班途中遭不明身份枪手袭击身亡，他的遗体刚被送往这家医院。<ref name=metro6054485/><ref>{{cite news|title=巴基斯坦医院遭袭93人亡 袭击者携带数公斤炸药|url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/08-08/7965552.shtml|accessdate=2016-08-11|agency=中新社|publisher=中新网|archive-date=2016-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811102727/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/08-08/7965552.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>多名律师和记者正在医院悼念和采访时，一名自杀式袭击者在急诊室外引爆炸弹。[[伊斯兰主义|伊斯兰]]组织[[巴基斯坦塔利班运动|巴基斯坦塔利班]]分支{{link-en|自由大会|Jamaat-ul-Ahrar}}（{{lang-ur|جماعت الاحرار}}）和[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]各自声称对袭击负责。

== 事件 ==
2016年8月8日早晨，俾路支省律师协会主席拉勒·安瓦尔·卡西[[律师|律师]]离家前往办公室，在Manno Jan路Mengal集市遭遇袭击。他的遗体被送到公立医院进行尸检，许多律师纷纷赶来，医院挤满了悼念者。就在此时，医院发生了一起疑似自杀式炸弹袭击，接着发生了枪击，导致多人死亡和受伤。<ref name="TOI"/><ref name="ET"/>

在奎达医院遭遇袭击和紧急情况后，警方和边境兵团接管了该地区。医院周围发现了[[手机干扰器|手机干扰器]]。警方表示，这是袭击者惯用手法，以此阻碍现场警方获取有关事态最新消息。排爆队报告说，袭击中使用了8到9公斤的爆炸物。25名律师和两名分别来自[[Aaj_新闻|Aaj 新闻]]和[[黎明新闻|黎明新闻]]的记者死于袭击，伤者中也包括许多律师和记者。<ref>{{cite news|title=巴基斯坦医院遭爆炸袭击70人亡 包括两名记者|url=http://ex.cssn.cn/gj/gj_gjzl/gj_ggzl/201608/t20160809_3155341.shtml|accessdate=2016-08-11|agency=京华时报|publisher=中国社会科学院网|archive-date=2016-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827153200/http://ex.cssn.cn/gj/gj_gjzl/gj_ggzl/201608/t20160809_3155341.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="TOI">{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/55-killed-over-100-injured-in-blast-at-hospital-in-Pakistans-Quetta/articleshow/53596823.cms|title=55 killed, over 100 injured in blast at hospital in Pakistan's Quetta|work=[[印度时报|印度时报]]|date=2016-08-08|accessdate=2016-08-10|archive-date=2016-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160808102728/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/55-killed-over-100-injured-in-blast-at-hospital-in-Pakistans-Quetta/articleshow/53596823.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ET">{{cite news|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/1157855/explosion-firing-heard-near-civil-hospital-quetta/|title=63 killed in blast at Quetta's civil hospital after lawyer's killing|work=论坛快报|date=2016-08-08|accessdate=2016-08-08|first=Zafar|last=Baloch|first2=Hasnaat|last2=Malik|first3=Sardar|last3=Sikandar|archive-date=2016-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160808061848/http://tribune.com.pk/story/1157855/explosion-firing-heard-near-civil-hospital-quetta/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 袭击者 ===
巴基斯坦塔利班和伊斯兰极端组织（ISIS）已声称对袭击事件负责。最初，伊斯兰国声称对袭击负责，“一名来自伊斯兰国的烈士，在奎达市司法部官员和巴基斯坦警察的一次集会上引爆了炸弹腰带。”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.newsweek.com/taliban-isis-both-claim-quetta-pakistan-hospital-suicide-bombing-488653 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-08-12 |archive-date=2016-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160812003634/http://www.newsweek.com/taliban-isis-both-claim-quetta-pakistan-hospital-suicide-bombing-488653 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="dawn"/><ref name="thenews">{{cite news|title=RAW-backed LeJ, TTP may have attacked Quetta|url=https://www.thenews.com.pk/print/141220-RAW-backed-LeJ-TTP-may-have-attacked-Quetta|accessdate=2016-08-09|work=www.thenews.com.pk|publisher=[[喀拉蚩新聞報|喀拉蚩新聞報]]|ref=thenews|archive-date=2016-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160812015439/https://www.thenews.com.pk/print/141220-RAW-backed-LeJ-TTP-may-have-attacked-Quetta|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，巴基斯坦武装组织巴基斯坦塔利班的一个分支{{link-en|自由大会|Jamaat-ul-Ahrar}}，也声称对袭击卡西律师和医院爆炸负责。<ref name="autogeneratedcivil"/><ref>{{cite web |author=Aamir Iqbal |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/suicide-bomber-targets-pakistans-lawyers-kills-at-least-53/2016/08/08/cce19344-5d4d-11e6-8e45-477372e89d78_story.html |title=Suicide blast claimed by Taliban faction in Pakistan claims at least 64 lives |publisher=[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]] |date=2016-08-08 |accessdate=2016-08-08 |archive-date=2016-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809174838/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/suicide-bomber-targets-pakistans-lawyers-kills-at-least-53/2016/08/08/cce19344-5d4d-11e6-8e45-477372e89d78_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Syed Ali Shah|url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1276183|title=70 dead as blast hits Quetta Civil Hospital after lawyer's killing|publisher=黎明新闻|date=2016-08-08|accessdate=2016-08-08|archive-date=2016-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809135428/http://www.dawn.com/news/1276183|dead-url=no}}</ref>该组织称将会发动更多袭击，“直至巴基斯坦实行伊斯兰制度”。<ref name="IE8Aug">{{cite web | url=http://indianexpress.com/article/world/world-news/balochistan-bomb-blast-in-civil-hospital-in-quetta-15-dead-2961150/ | title=Pakistani Taliban faction claims responsibility for Quetta hospital bomb blast that killed 75 | work=[[印度快报|印度快报]] | date=2016-08-08 | accessdate=2016-08-09 | author= | archive-date=2016-08-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809155249/http://indianexpress.com/article/world/world-news/balochistan-bomb-blast-in-civil-hospital-in-quetta-15-dead-2961150/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

